@page "/projects/projectlogo"
@using fishportfolio.Pages.Components

<PageTitle>Projects</PageTitle>
<MudContainer MaxWidth="MaxWidth.False" Class="ma-0 pa-0 d-flex flex-column justify-space-between">
    <MudPaper Class="px-8 py-4 mx-6 mb-6 align-self-center" Elevation="2" MinWidth="60vw" MaxWidth="800px">
        <Fishcrumbs />
        <MudText Class="ma-2" Color="Color.Secondary" Align="Align.Left" Typo="Typo.h1"><b>Logo project</b></MudText>
        <MudText Class="ma-2" Color="Color.Secondary" Align="Align.Left" Typo="Typo.body1">
            I needed a logo for myself to use on various projects of mine (including this site), so I designed one!
        </MudText>
        <MudDivider Style="background-color:#3aba9d; height:2px; opacity:0.7"></MudDivider>

        <MudGrid Spacing="1" Justify="Justify.Center">
            <MudItem xs="12" sm="12">
                <MudText Class="pa-0 ma-2" Color="Color.Secondary" Align="Align.Left" Typo="Typo.h2"><b>Getting started</b></MudText>
            </MudItem>
            <MudItem xs="12" sm="6">
                <MudText Class="pa-0 mx-2" Color="Color.Secondary" Align="Align.Left" Typo="Typo.body1">
                    First, I took a pencil and a sheet of paper and scribbled as many logo ideas as I could think of.
                    I let my mind go wild with designs, no matter how silly looking. This resulted in several designs I could compare and pick their best features to mold into one awesome logo 😃
                </MudText>
            </MudItem>
            <MudItem xs="12" sm="6">
                <MudContainer Class="pa-0 ma-0" MaxWidth="MaxWidth.False">
                    <MudImage Class="pa-0 ma-0" Fluid="true" ObjectFit="ObjectFit.Fill" Elevation="2" Src="./images/projectlogo/logo_draft_1.jpg" ObjectPosition="ObjectPosition.Center"></MudImage>
                    <MudText Class="d-flex justify-center" Color="Color.Secondary" Align="Align.Center" Typo="Typo.caption">This caption centers! 🥰</MudText>
                </MudContainer>
            </MudItem>







            <MudItem Class="pa-0" xs="12" sm="12">
                <MudText Class="pa-0 ma-2" Color="Color.Secondary" Align="Align.Right" Typo="Typo.h2"><b>Choosing the winner</b></MudText>
            </MudItem>
            <MudItem Class="pa-0" xs="12" sm="6">
                <MudContainer Class="pa-0 ma-2">
                    <MudImage Class="pa-0" Fluid ObjectFit="ObjectFit.Fill" Elevation="2" Src="./images/projectlogo/logo_draft_2.jpg" ObjectPosition="ObjectPosition.Center"></MudImage>
                    <MudText Class="d-flex justify-center" Color="Color.Secondary" Align="Align.Center" Typo="Typo.caption">This caption centers! 🥰</MudText>
                </MudContainer>
            </MudItem>
            <MudItem Class="pa-0" xs="12" sm="6">
                <MudContainer Class="pa-0 ma-0">
                    <MudText Class="pa-0 ma-2" Color="Color.Secondary" Align="Align.Right" Typo="Typo.body1">
                        I really liked the swirly seal one, so I decided to improve on it. I was satisfied with the final draft.
                    </MudText>
                </MudContainer>
            </MudItem>
        </MudGrid>
    </MudPaper>
</MudContainer>